text: Dino Lucchetta (born 13 March 1968) is an Italian rowing coxswain. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Italy Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Turin Category:Coxswains (rowing)
